## Arquitectura (patrón de módulos)

```
app.R
  └── shared (reactiveValues)
        ├── sf_data      ← vector (sf object)
        ├── raster_data  ← raster (SpatRaster)
        └── crs_info     ← CRS activo

  ├── mod_upload  → ESCRIBE en shared
  ├── mod_vector  → LEE de shared$sf_data
  ├── mod_raster  → LEE de shared$raster_data
  └── mod_stats   → LEE de ambos
```

